The '''Punta Negra Dam''' is a [[concrete-face rock-fill dam]] on the [[San Juan River (Argentina)|San Juan River]] about {{Convert|28|km}} west of [[San Juan, Argentina|San Juan]] in [[San Juan Province, Argentina|San Juan Province]], [[Argentina]]. The purpose of the dam is to provide water for irrigation and the generation of [[hydroelectric]] power. The {{Convert|101|m}} tall dam supports a {{convert|62|MW|adj=on}} power station and together with the [[Los Caracoles Dam]] upstream, it will provide for the irrigation of {{Convert|15000|ha}}. Construction began in 2009 and the dam and was finished in August 29, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|title=Beginning of the filling in Punta Negraâ€™s dam|url=http://www.techint-ingenieria.com/en/news/beginning-filling-punta-negras-dam|publisher=TECHINT|accessdate=11 February 2016}}</ref> It is being constructed immediately upstream of an diversion barrage.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.panedile.com.ar/archivos/Hidraulicas-in.pdf | title=Hydroelectric power plants | publisher=Panedile | accessdate=28 April 2014 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429045358/http://www.panedile.com.ar/archivos/Hidraulicas-in.pdf | archivedate=29 April 2014 | df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.obraspublicas.gov.ar/documentos/Libros_Respresas/Libro_Ingles.pdf | title=Hydroelectric Projects in the Santa Cruz River | work=Water and Energy National and Regional Integration | agency=Government of Argentina | page=97 | accessdate=28 April 2014 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429050346/http://www.obraspublicas.gov.ar/documentos/Libros_Respresas/Libro_Ingles.pdf | archivedate=29 April 2014 | df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bnamericas.com/news/electricpower/san-juan-provinces-punta-negra-dam-on-schedule-for-2015-startup | title=San Juan province's Punta Negra dam on schedule for 2015 startup | publisher=BN Americas | date=15 May 2012 | accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref>

